02:22.267 --> 02:25.729
<i>Grubhub, DoorDash, Uber Eats, and more,</i>

02:25.729 --> 02:30.025
<i>all competing to deliver
restaurant food to shut‐in consumers.</i>

02:30.025 --> 02:32.361
‐ When we have a pandemic,
delivery is a must.

02:32.361 --> 02:34.821
‐ This home delivery is moving
and it's moving right now.

02:34.821 --> 02:37.199
<i>The future of restaurants won't happen</i>

02:37.199 --> 02:39.201
<i>in the four walls
of a traditional restaurant.</i>

02:40.035 --> 02:42.204
<i>And as a restaurant owner,</i>

02:42.204 --> 02:44.164
<i>I don't know if we've quite fathomed</i>

02:44.164 --> 02:47.084
<i>just how much delivery
is gonna change the restaurant industry.</i>

