that it's not yet profitable.

08:07.070 --> 08:10.199
‐ The platforms themselves
lose a ton of money

08:10.199 --> 08:13.493
in the hundreds of millions of dollars,
billions collectively.

08:13.493 --> 08:15.495
‐ Why does this business even make sense?

08:15.495 --> 08:16.622
‐ I'm not sure it does.

08:27.799 --> 08:28.759
‐ Hey, AI.

08:30.385 --> 08:31.637
<i>You don't have to yell, Dave.</i>

08:31.637 --> 08:33.222
<i>I'm everywhere you want me to be.</i>

08:33.222 --> 08:34.556
‐ When did delivery start?

08:34.556 --> 08:36.850
<i>I see you're asking for help
hosting your TV show.</i>

08:36.850 --> 08:37.935
<i>That's no problem.</i>

08:37.935 --> 08:39.269
<i>My NASA scientist creators</i>

08:39.269 --> 08:41.730
<i>designed me to specifically address
queries like this</i>

08:41.730 --> 08:44.775
<i>because as a sentient AI foodie,
I know the whole story.</i>

08:45.901 --> 08:47.444
<i>Since the dawn of time,</i>

08:47.444 --> 08:49.404
<i>people have been trying
