09:06.630 --> 09:08.757
<i>though you can't really
get it there anymore for, um,</i>

09:08.757 --> 09:09.800
<i>reasons.</i>

09:09.800 --> 09:11.093
<i>But let's not get into that.</i>

09:11.093 --> 09:13.804
<i>These days, much of the conversation
around delivery</i>

09:13.804 --> 09:15.889
<i>revolves around apps and drones.</i>

