<i>But a lot of that
might just be smoke and mirrors,</i>

09:17.516 --> 09:20.227
<i>disguising what's still
a pretty rudimentary system.</i>

09:20.227 --> 09:22.479
<i>Is all this overkill?</i>

09:23.438 --> 09:24.940
<i>Great. Thanks, Elon.</i>

