09:32.239 --> 09:33.740
<i>started in the 19th century,</i>

09:33.740 --> 09:36.660
<i>so wives could send their husbands
a fresh, hot lunch from home.</i>

09:37.160 --> 09:39.079
<i>They deliver
hundreds of thousands of meals</i>

09:39.079 --> 09:41.456
<i>on time every time without an app.</i>

10:50.234 --> 10:51.276
Thank you.

11:40.701 --> 11:42.995
<i>People have been
delivering food for ages</i>

11:42.995 --> 11:44.246
<i>in all parts of the world.</i>

11:44.872 --> 11:48.375
<i>But what happens
when technology is part of the process?</i>

11:48.375 --> 11:51.587
<i>What happens to all of those people
