12:32.169 --> 12:34.087
not only am I fucked‐‐

12:34.087 --> 12:36.590
Have you seen <i>WALL‐E?</i>
‐ Exactly!

12:36.590 --> 12:38.342
It's <i>WALL‐E.</i>

12:38.342 --> 12:41.178
<i>Time for lunch in a cup!</i>

12:41.178 --> 12:43.347
‐ You know, like, you're driving around
in your own automatic car,

12:43.347 --> 12:45.140
