13:34.940 --> 13:39.528
<i>And eventually becoming assistant manager
and then general manager.</i>

13:39.528 --> 13:42.489
<i>And in some ways,
this is like a story of America.</i>

13:42.489 --> 13:45.367
It's something that I've seen
with a lot of people

